# Stopwatch Web Application

## Overview

This project is a Stopwatch Web Application developed during the SkillCraft Technology Web Development Internship. The application allows users to accurately measure time intervals and track lap timings.

## Features

- Start functionality
- Pause functionality
- Reset functionality
- Lap time tracking
- Responsive interface
- User-friendly design

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

## Project Structure

Task-02-Stopwatch-Web-App
│
├── index.html
├── style.css
├── script.js
└── assets

## How to Run

1. Download or clone the repository
2. Open the project folder
3. Run `index.html`

## Learning Outcomes

- JavaScript timing functions
- DOM manipulation
- Event listeners
- UI development

